  "texts": [
    "63 presented three classification techniques to group adult diffuse glioma patients into oligodendroglioma and astrocytoma classes.",
    "They obtained 75.0%, 80.0%, and 90.0% for ACC using a weighted average-based classification method.",
    "Dropout enables ensemble learning for multi-scale image classification and DenseNet-161 network for classifying low-grade gliomas.",
    "To further improve the evaluation robustness of our model, we have applied k-fold cross-validation with 10 folds.",
    "Using this method, the data is split into ten distinct folds, each of which is used at different stages for training and validation."
  ],
